{
  "texts": [
    "As evident in the figure, all VAE-based methods successfully disregard the anomalies during reconstruction.",
    "However, the reconstruction results for some normal points, particularly those marked by a blue rectangle ① and ellipse ④, are not satisfactory.",
    "This substantially impacts the overall performance, leading us to identify three key challenges that we address in the subsequent sections.",
    "Challenge 1: Capturing similar yet heterogeneous periodic patterns.",
    "From Figure 1, periodic patterns can be observed in the curves, with one such period emphasized by the red shaded area ②."
  ]
}